>
<ParallaxHeader client:idle />
<div style="margin: 50px">
<section>
  <h1>Range Repair in Los ANgeles and Nearby Areas</h1>
  <p><strong>Trusted Experts in Luxury Range Service & Restoration</strong></p>
  <p>When your luxury range stops performing at its best, it’s more than just an inconvenience — it interrupts the rhythm of your home. At Zaricci, we understand the level of craftsmanship behind premium appliances, and we treat every service call with the same precision and care your range was built with.</p>
  <p>Whether you’re a private chef in Bel Air or a design-savvy homeowner in Malibu, we bring white-glove service to your doorstep — same day, discreet, and highly skilled.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>⭐ Specializing in Premium Range Brands</h3>
  <p>Our certified technicians are trained to diagnose and repair the world’s most exclusive range brands, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>La Cornue</li>
    <li>Wolf</li>
    <li>Viking</li>
    <li>Bertazzoni</li>
    <li>Dacor</li>
    <li>Gaggenau</li>
    <li>Thermador</li>
    <li>Miele</li>
    <li>Monogram</li>
    <li>BlueStar</li>
    <li>Fisher &amp; Paykel</li>
    <li>Smeg</li>
  </ul>
  <p>From malfunctioning igniters to precision temperature calibration, we restore your range to showroom condition — and we do it with respect for your home, your time, and your lifestyle.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>🔍 Common Range Issues We Resolve</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Burners that won’t ignite or heat unevenly</li>
    <li>Gas smell or pilot light issues</li>
    <li>Oven not maintaining temperature</li>
    <li>Digital display or control panel malfunction</li>
    <li>Broken knobs, hinges, or custom finishes</li>
    <li>Electrical surges affecting smart features</li>
    <li>Professional-grade ventilation issues</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>💼 What to Expect with Zaricci</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Same-Day Luxury Repair in most areas of Los Angeles, Ventura &amp; Orange County</li>
    <li>Certified Technicians trained on luxury &amp; European models</li>
    <li>Genuine Parts &amp; invisible touchups for premium finishes</li>
    <li>Discreet Service that respects your space and schedule</li>
    <li>Follow-Up Support to ensure your appliance performs beautifully</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>🏠 Where We Operate</h3>
  <p>We proudly serve luxury estates, designer homes, and commercial residences in:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Beverly Hills</li>
    <li>Malibu</li>
    <li>Bel Air</li>
    <li>Pasadena</li>
    <li>Newport Beach</li>
    <li>Calabasas</li>
    <li>Brentwood</li>
    <li>and more</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>🛠️ Preventative Maintenance for High-End Ranges</h3>
  <p>Luxury appliances are an investment. We offer custom maintenance packages to preserve peak performance, extend lifespan, and avoid costly breakdowns — all scheduled around your convenience.</p>
</section>
</div>
